description: Urban Style Loft Living in Fort Point Channel. Authentic brick and beam architecture, efficient layout with flex floor plan. Wood flooring,13' beam wood ceilings, soaring sun filled insulated windows with electronic custom black out shades. Space allows for home office or dine area, sleek kitchen w/S.S. appliances, zebra wood finished cabinetry offering honed black granite countertops. Queen size Murphy bed -shelving -cabinets and lighting on light stand. Spa like spacious bathroom tile shower and glass door, shelf under sink. Spacious custom walk-in closet, central air, laundry in-unit, hall closet. Expansive common roof deck with breathtaking City scape views.Boutique entry with intercom, chairlift, elevated building, private lower level storage and secured bike area. Neighborhood central located to So Station-Amtrac,Financial and Seaport Districts, short walk to Boston harbor retail shops, bus lines and underground trains. Many trendy restaurants and shopping near by.
